{"data":[{"date":"09:25 01/07","title":"\u0110\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, HLV Uruguay \"n\u1ed5\" t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/da-bai-bo-dao-nha-hlv-uruguay-no-tung-bung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup n\u0103m nay. V\u00e0 HLV Oscar Tabarez m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u0129.</h2><h2>Tabarez \u201cn\u1ed5\u201d to sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uruguay hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u201cng\u1ef1a \u00f4\u201d c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Oscar Tabarez \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1i Sochi \u0111\u00eam qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCavani l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Uruguay \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a PSG ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec5n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, HLV Tabarez n\u1ed5 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, HLV Tabarez n\u1ed5 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/da-bai-bo-dao-nha-hlv-uruguay-no-tung-bung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Uruguay s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Ph\u00e1p. V\u00e0 HLV Tabarez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ng\u1ea1i Les Bleus khi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn th\u1eb3ng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\u201d, </em>Tabarez chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Fisht Stadium.</div>\r\n<h2>Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u0129 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng \u00edt h\u01a1n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u00ec ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Uruguay v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng, Tabarez cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 World Cup \u1edf Nam Phi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng duy nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n Nam Phi. Khi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 4 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea7m t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i Italia. \u0110\u00f4i khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fac b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. V\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u th\u00ec b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng trong s\u1ebd ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cavani-len-tieng-ve-chan-thuong-trong-tran-thang-bo-dao-nha-421-190065.html\">Cavani l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-21-bdn-ngay-ronaldo-phai-ghen-ti-voi-song-sat-suarez-cavani-421-190051.html\">Uruguay 2-1 B\u0110N: Ng\u00e0y Ronaldo ph\u1ea3i ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi \u201csong s\u00e1t\u201d Suarez \u2013 Cavani</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"775","checkdouble":"190071"},{"date":"10:01 01/07","title":"Colombia n\u1eeda m\u1eebng n\u1eeda lo v\u1ec1 James Rodriguez tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 1/8","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/colombia-nua-mung-nua-lo-ve-james-rodriguez-truoc-vong-18.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a James Rodriguez kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra s\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 cho Colombia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.</h2><h2>James Rodriguez kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">James \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp t\u1ec5nh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Colombia v\u00e0 Senegal. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u0129 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out, \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 T\u01b0 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9, Colombia n\u1eeda m\u1eebng n\u1eeda lo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"James Rodriguez ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9, Colombia n\u1eeda m\u1eebng n\u1eeda lo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/colombia-nua-mung-nua-lo-ve-james-rodriguez-truoc-vong-18.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>James Rodriguez ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nColombia \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn trong m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y r\u1eb1ng James \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i ch\u1ee5p chi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a James l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cNh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cho th\u1ea5y James b\u1ecb s\u01b0ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng g\u00ec v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 \u1edf ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i\u201d</em>, Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Colombia cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng vi\u1ec7c James Rodriguez kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb r\u00e1ch c\u01a1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Colombia. Nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c ch\u00e2n b\u1ecb s\u01b0ng t\u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJames Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng \u1edf World Cup 2014 t\u1ea1i Brazil. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Colombia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi t\u1eadn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Colombia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. N\u1ebfu l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Los Cafeteros ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. B\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nColombia d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd t\u1eadp k\u00edn v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0o 1h ng\u00e0y 4/7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Colombia:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-chelsea-theo-duoi-ngoi-sao-dt-colombia-172-189966.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tran-colombia-se-la-cuoc-dau-knockout-lon-nhat-thap-ky-cua-anh-421-189909.html\">Tr\u1eadn Colombia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 c\u1ee7a Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"774","checkdouble":"190072"},{"date":"10:50 01/07","title":"Neville khen ng\u1ee3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 10 t\u1edbi v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018.</h2><h2>K\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u, th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng t\u1ea1o c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i Bahrain khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u \u00c1. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n b\u1edfi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u00ec l\u1ee3m v\u00e0 ngoan c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t xa t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U19 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y \u00c1 l\u00e0 U.A.E v\u00e0 Iraq.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 cho tham v\u1ecdng World Cu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 cho tham v\u1ecdng World Cu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/28/U19-Viet-Nam-vs-U19-Thai-Lan-Buoc-chay-da-cho-tham-vong-World-Cu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi k\u1ef3 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Bahrain. V\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean c\u00fa s\u1ed1c ti\u1ebfp theo khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Tr\u1ea7n Th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n s\u1edf h\u1eefu 1 trong 4 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 n\u0103m sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u1edbi th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng s\u1ebd t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u00e0 l\u1ee9a Quang H\u1ea3i, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu,&hellip; \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Bahrain n\u0103m 2016. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eebng c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c hay Morocco c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a \u0111\u00e0n anh hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed5i nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan - c\u1ed1 nh\u00e2n h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup 2019 b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 1/7 t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, trong khu v\u1ef1c, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf m\u1ecdi c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9, t\u1eeb \u0110TQG cho t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2015, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng 0-6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"u19 thai lan\" title=\"u19 th\u00e1i lan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/30/micki-khong-hieu-noi-mourinho-dang-nghi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U19 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U18 \u0110N\u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eafng khi b\u1ecb Myanmar v\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111\u00e1 v\u0103ng kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, trong khi U18 Th\u00e1i Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ea5y tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111ang nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ecf ra e ng\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Th\u00e1i Lan c\u0169ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1eeb 3, 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea3.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c em khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho d\u00f9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p Th\u00e1i Lan, Indonesia hay Philippines&quot;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u1eef v\u1eefng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018:&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 1/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 3/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Philippines (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 5/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 L\u00e0o (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 19h00, 7/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Indonesia (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 8/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Singapore (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-khong-ngai-u19-thai-lan-o-ngay-ra-quan-u19-dna-168-189953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-khong-ngai-u19-thai-lan-o-ngay-ra-quan-u19-dna.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-khong-ngai-u19-thai-lan-o-ngay-ra-quan-u19-dna-168-189953.html\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-168-189289.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-168-189289.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i xem nh\u1eb9 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan, Narakorn Noomchansakul \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-tre-ha-noi-ap-dao-doi-hinh-u19-viet-nam-du-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-168-189877.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/9/doi-tre-ha-noi-ap-dao-doi-hinh-u19-viet-nam-du-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-tre-ha-noi-ap-dao-doi-hinh-u19-viet-nam-du-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-168-189877.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"773","checkdouble":"190073"},{"date":"11:25 01/07","title":"S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i binh t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Eden Hazard \u1edf \u0110T B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/sai-gon-fc-chieu-mo-ngoai-binh-tung-choi-cung-eden-hazard-o-dt-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau chu\u1ed7i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110T B\u1ec9, Marvin Ogunjimi.</h2><h2>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i binh Marvin Ogunjimi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marvin Ogunjimi cap ben Sai Gon FC\" title=\"Marvin Ogunjimi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/sai-gon-fc-chieu-mo-ngoai-binh-tung-choi-cung-eden-hazard-o-dt-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Marvin Ogunjimi (tr\u00e1i) c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 16 v\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 chung cu\u1ed9c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC sa s\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay v\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chia tay HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh mang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, BL\u0110 CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Marvin Ogunjimi - ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd chia l\u1eeda tr\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Da Sylva trong 10 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sinh n\u0103m 1987, Marvin Ogunjimi&nbsp;c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n l\u00ed l\u1ecbch kh\u00e1 &lsquo;ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng&rsquo; khi t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o U18, U19 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 \u0110TQG B\u1ec9&nbsp;trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian 2010-2011. Anh \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh hi\u1ec7n nay trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T B\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard, Fellaini, Kompany&hellip; Trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, Marvin c\u00f3 7 tr\u1eadn kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u00e0y, t\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng&nbsp;cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u1eadu ta m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 30/6. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian xem Marvin Ogunjimi ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, do m\u1edbi h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 17, Marvin Ogunjimi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-nam-dinh-18h00-ngay-17-vleague-2018-344-190057.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-nam-dinh-18h00-ngay-17-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-nam-dinh-18h00-ngay-17-vleague-2018-344-190057.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 18h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7 (V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nS\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00fac 18h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7 (V\u00f2ng 17 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"772","checkdouble":"190074"},{"date":"11:14 01/07","title":"Liverpool tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ee5 Fekir, quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/liverpool-tro-lai-vu-fekir-quyet-canh-tranh-voi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Fekir, quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Man United cho ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</h2><h2>MU nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Fekir</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 mang Fekir v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u01b0u ti\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Fekir.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Le Progres c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Fekir \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Manchester United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Man United nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Fekir c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. Nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng MU kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u. V\u00e0 Fekir th\u00ec \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t vi\u00ean ng\u1ecdc qu\u00fd ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Fekir\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi MU v\u1ee5 Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi MU v\u1ee5 Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/liverpool-tro-lai-vu-fekir-quyet-canh-tranh-voi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi MU v\u1ee5 Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-da-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-tan-binh-thu-3-172-188022.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fekir t\u1eebng ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Liverpool</span> v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Anfield. Nh\u01b0ng The Kop l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Lyon. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Fekir s\u1ebd t\u0103ng v\u1ecdt sau World Cup v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng t\u1edd Daily Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 quay l\u1ea1i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Fekir m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Fekir sau khi World Cup kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn \u0111ang gi\u00e0nh pole trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Fekir kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u1ea1i sao c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool \u01b0? V\u00ec th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1c, t\u1edd Daily Mirror c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Ings \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia tay s\u00e2n Anfield \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u00e1c. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ra s\u00e2n 8 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Crystal Palace v\u00e0 Newcastle United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Premier League:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-chelsea-theo-duoi-ngoi-sao-dt-colombia-172-189966.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/marco-asensio-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-liverpool-172-189656.html\">Marco Asensio c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"771","checkdouble":"190075"},{"date":"10:57 01/07","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Th\u00e1i Lan: B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 cho tham v\u1ecdng World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/u19-viet-nam-dau-u19-thai-lan-buoc-chay-da-cho-tham-vong-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 10 t\u1edbi v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018.</h2><h2>K\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u, th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng t\u1ea1o c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i Bahrain khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u \u00c1. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n b\u1edfi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u00ec l\u1ee3m v\u00e0 ngoan c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t xa t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U19 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y \u00c1 l\u00e0 U.A.E v\u00e0 Iraq.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 cho tham v\u1ecdng World Cu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 cho tham v\u1ecdng World Cu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/28/U19-Viet-Nam-vs-U19-Thai-Lan-Buoc-chay-da-cho-tham-vong-World-Cu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi k\u1ef3 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Bahrain. V\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean c\u00fa s\u1ed1c ti\u1ebfp theo khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Tr\u1ea7n Th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n s\u1edf h\u1eefu 1 trong 4 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 n\u0103m sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u1edbi th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng s\u1ebd t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u00e0 l\u1ee9a Quang H\u1ea3i, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu,&hellip; \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Bahrain n\u0103m 2016. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eebng c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c hay Morocco c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a \u0111\u00e0n anh hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed5i nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan - c\u1ed1 nh\u00e2n h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup 2019 b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 1/7 t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, trong khu v\u1ef1c, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf m\u1ecdi c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9, t\u1eeb \u0110TQG cho t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2015, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng 0-6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"u19 thai lan\" title=\"u19 th\u00e1i lan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/30/micki-khong-hieu-noi-mourinho-dang-nghi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U19 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U18 \u0110N\u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eafng khi b\u1ecb Myanmar v\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111\u00e1 v\u0103ng kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, trong khi U18 Th\u00e1i Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ea5y tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111ang nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ecf ra e ng\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Th\u00e1i Lan c\u0169ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1eeb 3, 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea3.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c em khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho d\u00f9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p Th\u00e1i Lan, Indonesia hay Philippines&quot;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u1eef v\u1eefng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018:&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 1/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 3/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Philippines (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 5/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 L\u00e0o (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 19h00, 7/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Indonesia (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 8/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Singapore (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-khong-ngai-u19-thai-lan-o-ngay-ra-quan-u19-dna-168-189953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-khong-ngai-u19-thai-lan-o-ngay-ra-quan-u19-dna.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-khong-ngai-u19-thai-lan-o-ngay-ra-quan-u19-dna-168-189953.html\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-168-189289.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-168-189289.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i xem nh\u1eb9 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan, Narakorn Noomchansakul \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-tre-ha-noi-ap-dao-doi-hinh-u19-viet-nam-du-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-168-189877.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/9/doi-tre-ha-noi-ap-dao-doi-hinh-u19-viet-nam-du-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-tre-ha-noi-ap-dao-doi-hinh-u19-viet-nam-du-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-168-189877.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"770","checkdouble":"190076"},{"date":"10:56 01/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan 15h30 ng\u00e0y 1/7 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-15h30-ngay-17.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 l\u00fac 15h30 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 14/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f9ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia, \u0110KV\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan, Singapore, Philippines v\u00e0 L\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng khi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhau. Do \u0111\u00f3, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e1 k\u1ef9 cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan 15h30 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay 17 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan 15h30 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay 17 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-u19-tl.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan</h2>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 6 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande (Trung Qu\u1ed1c). C\u00f2n h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ecd x\u00e1t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U19 Suwon JS Cup 2018 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i U19 Mexico (thua 0-4), U19 Morocco (1-1) v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (1-1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n T\u1edbi, B\u00f9i Ho\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t Anh, Nguy\u1ec5n Xu\u00e2n Ki\u00ean, L\u00ea V\u0103n Xu\u00e2n, Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n, Tr\u1ea7n C\u00f4ng Minh... <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam, l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ng\u1eafn, ban b\u1eadt nh\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ec1u nay, khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ed3i ch\u1edd U19 Th\u00e1i Lan h\u1edf s\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2017, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch. V\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1i t\u00ean U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN C\u1ee6A U19&nbsp; VI\u1ec6T NAM:</strong> Y \u00ca Li Ni \u00ca; V\u0103n Xu\u00e2n, V\u0103n T\u1edbi, Vi\u1ec7t Anh, Quang Vinh; H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n, V\u0103n C\u00f4ng, C\u00f4ng Minh, H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng, Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa, V\u0103n Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018:&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 1/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 3/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Philippines (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 5/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 L\u00e0o (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 19h00, 7/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Indonesia (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 8/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Singapore (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan 15h30 ng\u00e0y 17 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan 15h30 ng\u00e0y 17 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/TRUC-TIEP-U19-Viet-Nam-vs-U19-Thai-Lan-15h30-ngay-17-(U19-Dong-Nam-A-2018)-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Danh s\u00e1ch U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-dau-u19-thai-lan-buoc-chay-da-cho-tham-vong-world-cup-168-190076.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/u19-viet-nam-dau-u19-thai-lan-buoc-chay-da-cho-tham-vong-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-dau-u19-thai-lan-buoc-chay-da-cho-tham-vong-world-cup-168-190076.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Th\u00e1i Lan: B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 cho tham v\u1ecdng World Cup</span><br>\r\n\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 10 t\u1edbi v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup hai n\u0103m...</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"769","checkdouble":"190078"},{"date":"11:06 01/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 - B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng BXH - LT\u0110 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.</h2>T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 6 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3ng B d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo lu\u1eadt, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f2ng tr\u00f2n 1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t, ch\u1ecdn ra 2 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t - nh\u00ec m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e9o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 chung k\u1ebft. Theo l\u1ecbch, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 2 ng\u00e0y /tr\u1eadn, m\u1edf m\u00e0n l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam l\u00e0 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u1ecd x\u00e1t, th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 r\u00e0 so\u00e1t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 18/10 \u0111\u1ebfn 4/11/2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng nam \u00c1 2018:<br>\r\nB\u1ea3ng A: Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Th\u00e1i Lan, Indonesia, Singapore, L\u00e0o, Philippines;<br>\r\nB\u1ea3ng B: Malaysia, Timor Leste, Myanmar, Campuchia, Brunei.<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; widt